#####################################################

Instruction to compile and install the Syu_Cstr code, the functionality of which is to construct simulation system
(Simple Cubic, Body Centered Cubic, Face Centered Cubic, 2D hexagonal crystal, cubic diamond structure, zincblende
structure.

#####################################################

Installation: By typing "make", Sys_Cstry will be automatically installled under the directory of QMTIS/bin. You may
make changes of the default c-compilor, path of compiled executable file.

